Sometimes [[Tor_Browser#Tor_Browser_Downloader_by_Whonix_.E2.84.A2|Tor Browser Downloader]] inside {{workstation_product_name}} breaks because torproject.org changes the way Tor Browser can be downloaded or verified. This program is maintained by the [[Contributors|{{project_name}} contributors]] and The Tor Project is not responsible for necessary fixes. Generally, [http://forums.whonix.org/c/news {{project_name}} news] will be published within a few days with working instructions on how to fix the problem. If this does not happen, then {{project_name}} developers are unaware of the issue. 

